column.name: remote_id
column.Comment: share ID at the remote server

column.name: remote
column.Comment: Url of the remove owncloud instance

column.name: password
column.Comment: Optional password for the public share

column.name: name
column.Comment: Original name on the remote server

column.name: owner
column.Comment: User that owns the public share on the remote server

column.name: user
column.Comment: Local user which added the external share

column.name: mountpoint
column.Comment: Full path where the share is mounted

column.name: url_hash
column.Comment: sha1 hash of the url without the protocol

column.name: token
column.Comment: token used to exchange the shared secret
